import React from 'react'
import Tabs from 'shared/tabs'
import Card from 'shared/card'
import Ranking from './components/Ranking'
const { TabList, Tab, TabPanels, TabPanel } = Tabs

const Rankings = () => {
  return (
    <Card>
      <Tabs>
        <TabList isToggle>
          <Tab>Clientes</Tab>
          <Tab>Proveedores</Tab>
        </TabList>
        <TabPanels>
          <TabPanel>
            <Ranking type='income' />
          </TabPanel>
          <TabPanel>
            <Ranking type='expense' />
          </TabPanel>
        </TabPanels>
      </Tabs>
    </Card>
  )
}

export default Rankings
